🏷️ Project Title

# Bookkeeping MCP Server
📦 Description

A custom MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for managing bookkeeping tasks such as generating reports, invoices, and summaries. Built using `mcp[cli]` and powered by Claude Desktop.

🚀 Installation
## Prerequisites
- Python 3.13+
- `uv` package manager
- Claude Desktop installed

## Setup
```bash
pip install uv
uv init bookkeeping-mcp-server
cd bookkeeping-mcp-server
uv add "mcp[cli]"

🧠 Usage
uv run mcp install main.py

